platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: With its gorgeous photos and step-by-step instructions, this compilation of more than 15,000 recipes from The New York Times’ vaults belongs in every kitchen. We love how easy it is to save and search for recipes, and themed collections like “Easy Cakes,” “Beer Cocktails,” and “A Taste of New Orleans” are a mouthwatering delight. The app also features dozens of short instructional videos on topics like trussing chicken and julienning peppers—perfect for novice chefs eager to dive in and start cooking.
這款 App 收錄超過 15,000 款食譜，同時讓你能輕鬆儲存和搜尋，並提供主題系列食譜和教學影片，非常適合剛接觸烹飪的新手廚師。
This compilation of more than 15,000 recipes features easy saving and searching, with themed collections and instructional videos – perfect for novice chefs eager to start cooking.
保存や検索が簡単にできる、15,000種類以上のレシピをテーマ別に集めたコレクションです。作り方の動画も付属しているので、料理に挑戦したいと思っている初心者におすすめです。
This compilation of more than 15,000 recipes features easy saving and searching, with themed collections and instructional videos–perfect for novice chefs eager to start cooking.
這款 App 收錄了超過 15,000 份食譜，並附有主題食譜集和教學影片，無論是保存或搜尋都非常簡單，很適合廚藝新手。
Une compilation de plus de 15 000 recettes faciles à sauvegarder et à trouver, avec des collections thématiques et des tutos vidéo. C’est parfait pour les novices qui se mettent aux fourneaux.
带上这款烹饪指南，开启奇妙厨房之旅。App 汇编了超过两万个食谱，方便你保存搜索。心血来潮想制作一道西班牙特色美食？别担心，详细的教学视频能帮助新手厨师快速上手。

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Get started on the big meal with beautiful photos and with step-by-step instructions.
